text: Carancho is a 2010 Argentine Chilean French South Korean crime drama movie directed by Pablo Trapero and starring Ricardo Darín, Martina Gusmán. It was nominated for the Un Certain Regard at the 2010 Cannes Film Festival. == Other websites == * * * Category:2010 crime drama movies Category:Argentine crime movies Category:Argentine drama movies Category:Chilean movies Category:French crime movies Category:French drama movies Category:South Korean movies
